CTabFolderRenderer:
* Remove curve-related fields (curve, curveWidth, curveIndent, etc.).
* Remove selection highlight caching and associated gradient methods.
* Delete obsolete no-op methods including updateCurves(), drawHighlight(), and disposeSelectionHighlightGradientColors().
* Simplify rendering logic:
  - Replace all corner constants with EMPTY_CORNER.
  - Enforce square corners regardless of the 'simple' flag.
  - Streamline drawTabArea and border rendering methods.
  - Remove curve-related width adjustments from computeTrim.
  - Remove anti-aliasing logic (unnecessary for square tabs).
* Force useEllipses() to always return true.

Fixes https://github.com/eclipse-platform/eclipse.platform.swt/issues/3150

